
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Careers | Your Company</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #dfdff5 /* Blue header */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .job-listing {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

            .job-listing:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

        .job-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .job-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .apply-btn {
            background-color: #28a745; /* Green button */
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .apply-btn:hover {
                background-color: #218838; /* Darker green on hover */
            }

        .footer-career {
            background-color: #dfdff5;
            color: navy;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1 style="font-weight:bold">Careers at JX Travels</h1>
        <p>Join us in creating innovative solutions!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="job-listing">
            <div class="job-title">Software Engineer</div>
            <div class="job-description">Develop and maintain software applications.</div>
            <a href="#" class="apply-btn">Apply Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="job-listing">
            <div class="job-title">Marketing Specialist</div>
            <div class="job-description">Create marketing campaigns and strategies.</div>
            <a href="#" class="apply-btn">Apply Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="job-listing">
            <div class="job-title">Sales Manager</div>
            <div class="job-description">Lead sales team and drive revenue growth.</div>
            <a href="#" class="apply-btn">Apply Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-career">
        <p>&copy; 2024 JX Travels. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>